text: The Vänersborg Church () is a church building in the central parts of the town of Vänersborg in Sweden. It belongs to the Vänersborg and Väne-Ryr Parish of the Church of Sweden. The church was built between 1783 and 1784. It was inaugurated on 5 August 1784. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Church of Sweden churches Category:18th-century buildings and structures Category:Vänersborg
title: Vänersborg Church
